<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Risques & Obsolescence — Executive IT</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&display=swap');

    :root {
      --navy: #0a192f;
      --gold: #c5a059;
      --slate: #64748b;
      --border: #e2e8f0;
      --bg-light: #f8fafc;
      --white: #ffffff;
      /* Couleurs de risque sémantiques */
      --critical: #991b1b;
      --high: #dc2626;
      --medium: #f59e0b;
      --low: #10b981;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: var(--bg-light); color: var(--navy); }

    .dashboard-container { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr; min-height: 100vh; }

    /* Sidebar - Identique à la Charte */
    .sidebar { background: var(--navy); color: white; padding: 40px 20px; }
    .nav-link { padding: 12px 15px; border-radius: 4px; color: #cbd5e1; cursor: pointer; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 13px; }
    .nav-link.active { background: var(--gold); color: var(--navy); font-weight: 700; }

    /* Content */
    .content { padding: 50px; max-width: 1300px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; }
    
    .header-risk { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; margin-bottom: 40px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--navy); padding-bottom: 20px; }
    .btn-report { background: var(--navy); color: white; border: none; padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 2px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }

    /* Matrix 2x2 Visual */
    .risk-matrix-container {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 40px 1fr 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 40px;
      gap: 10px;
      height: 450px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .axis-y { writing-mode: vertical-lr; transform: rotate(180deg); text-align: center; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--slate); text-transform: uppercase; }
    .axis-x { grid-column: 2 / 4; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--slate); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 15px; }
    
    .matrix-cell {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 20px;
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .cell-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    
    /* Quadrants */
    .q-extreme { background: rgba(153, 27, 27, 0.05); border-top: 4px solid var(--critical); }
    .q-high { background: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.03); border-top: 4px solid var(--high); }
    .q-managed { background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.03); border-top: 4px solid var(--medium); }
    .q-safe { background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.03); border-top: 4px solid var(--low); }

    /* Risk Items */
    .risk-tag { 
      background: var(--white); 
      border: 1px solid var(--border); 
      padding: 6px 10px; 
      font-size: 11px; 
      margin-bottom: 5px; 
      display: inline-block;
      box-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    /* Obsolescence Heatmap */
    .grid-panels { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr; gap: 30px; margin-top: 30px; }
    .card { background: white; padding: 25px; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .card-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display'; font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold); display: inline-block; padding-bottom: 5px; }

    .obs-list { list-style: none; }
    .obs-item { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; }
    .status-dot { width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 10px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="dashboard-container">
  <aside class="sidebar">
    <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display'; margin-bottom: 30px;">EXECUTIVE <span style="color:var(--gold)">SI</span></h2>
    <div class="nav-link">Vue d'ensemble</div>
    <div class="nav-link">Portefeuille Apps</div>
    <div class="nav-link">Gestion Financière</div>
    <div class="nav-link active">Risques & Obsolescence</div>
    <div class="nav-link">Sourcing</div>
  </aside>

  <main class="content">
    <header class="header-risk">
      <div>
        <h1 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display'; font-size: 32px;">Technology Risk Management</h1>
        <p style="color: var(--slate); font-size: 14px;">Évaluation de l'exposition et trajectoires de remédiation</p>
      </div>
      <button class="btn-report">Générer Rapport Risque</button>
    </header>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Matrice de Criticité des Actifs</div>
      <div class="risk-matrix-container">
        <div class="axis-y">Impact Métier (Sévérité)</div>
        
        <div class="matrix-cell q-extreme">
          <span class="cell-label" style="color: var(--critical)">Zone de Rupture (Action immédiate)</span>
          <div>
            <div class="risk-tag">ERP Core Legacy (V.2012)</div>
            <div class="risk-tag">Mainframe HR Data</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="matrix-cell q-high">
          <span class="cell-label" style="color: var(--high)">Risques Stratégiques</span>
          <div>
            <div class="risk-tag">Passerelle de Paiement</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="matrix-cell q-managed">
          <span class="cell-label" style="color: var(--medium)">Dette Technique à Gérer</span>
          <div>
            <div class="risk-tag">Serveurs Print & File</div>
            <div class="risk-tag">Outil Ticketing N3</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="matrix-cell q-safe">
          <span class="cell-label" style="color: var(--low)">Zone de Veille</span>
          <div>
            <div class="risk-tag">Portail Intranet</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="axis-x">Probabilité d'Occurrence / Obsolescence</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-panels">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Top 5 - Alertes Fin de Support (EOS)</div>
        <ul class="obs-list">
          <li class="obs-item">
            <span><strong>Windows Server 2012 R2</strong> <br><small>14 instances restantes</small></span>
            <span style="color: var(--critical); font-weight: 700;">Q2 2026</span>
          </li>
          <li class="obs-item">
            <span><strong>Oracle DB 12c</strong> <br><small>Base de données CRM</small></span>
            <span style="color: var(--high); font-weight: 700;">Q4 2026</span>
          </li>
          <li class="obs-item">
            <span><strong>SAP Business Suite 7</strong> <br><small>Maintenance mainstream</small></span>
            <span style="color: var(--medium); font-weight: 700;">2027</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="background: var(--navy); color: white;">
        <div class="card-title" style="color: var(--gold); border-color: var(--gold);">Recommandations</div>
        <p style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
          L'exposition majeure se concentre sur le <strong>Core ERP</strong>. Un arbitrage budgétaire de <strong>1.2M€</strong> est requis pour sécuriser la transition vers le Cloud avant la fin de support Q2.
        </p>
        <div style="padding: 15px; border-left: 2px solid var(--gold); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">
          <span style="font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold);">Prochaine Étape</span>
          <p style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;">Validation du plan de migration en CODIR le 15/04.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</div>

</body>
</html>
